kit
===

Syntax: kit
        apprentice

Apprentice-only tool. Pick a staff track, draft the small task for that
track, and submit it for domain review.

  1. Choose track (rp / domain / coding)
  2. View task brief
  3. Draft / edit submission
  4. Submit to domain queue
  5. View my submission status

Domain wizards review via domain option 10.
Coding wizards review the coding queue via: review

Ready for setrole is a flag only. An admin must still run setrole.

See also: help apprentice *wizard staff, help setrole
